<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
   .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .logo {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .logo img {
        width: 350px;
        height: auto;
    }

    .header {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #007bff;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .reset-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background-color: #006ad5; 
    color: #fff; 
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: background-color 0.3s; 
}

    .reset-link:hover {
        background-color: rgb(25, 57, 199); 
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .action-button {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
            padding: 10px;
        }
    }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://w7.pngwing.com/pngs/270/728/png-transparent-iron-man-stark-industries-logo-decal-marvel-comics-industry-angle-superhero-text-thumbnail.png"
                alt="Company Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="header">Password Reset Request</div>
        <div class="subtitle">Dear user,</div>
        <div class="subtitle">I am FRYDAY,</div>
        <p>You have requested to reset your password. Click the link below to reset your password:</p>
        <div class="action-button">
            <a href="{{ resetPasswordLink }}" class="reset-link">Reset Password</a>
        </div>
        <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
        <hr>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #777;">Please note: This is a system-generated email. Do not reply to this
            email as we are unable to receive messages sent to this address.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
